{"id": 1092, "genre": 1000, "title": "你在什么时候发现自我认知出现了偏差？", "description": "生活中那些让你疑问“这真是我吗？”的时刻。（题图来自：Jun Cen）", "record_count": 7066, "comment_count": 24, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160719223656rKYsxo2ytw70PZWu.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-07-19T17:00:02Z", "questions": [{"id": 973, "title": "你在什么时候发现自我认知出现了偏差？", "content": "你在什么时候发现自我认知出现了偏差？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 95361, "content": "觉得自己声音很好听，听自己微信语音才发现怎么这么难听", "image": "img/option/option/201607051707582rxGpLAeUl4OcMui.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 95363, "content": "打游戏感觉队友都是垃圾时，突然意识到这是一个匹配机制", "image": "img/option/option/20160705170651b8y91jfP47su0mnW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 95364, "content": "看自己以前的动态觉得非常矫情", "image": "img/option/option/20160705170551rEG6cFCXyPLWn3fs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 95365, "content": "我自拍时都很美，被别人拍怎么就那么丑", "image": "img/option/option/20160705170505RT3PCkEU4oxuGqJh.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 95366, "content": "导购：“你身材比例好，肤色也白皙...”，你说的真的是我吗？", "image": "img/option/option/201607051704142jBEnYkodzNXsfQx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 95367, "content": "理发师剪了一个巨丑的发型然后说......很适合你", "image": "img/option/option/20160705170314caSl0kspedFvWhHP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 96177, "content": "某些App（看似）智能地推送给你“两性”、“养生”类文章", "image": "img/option/option/20160708060138e6NlRUvBSV85p0zj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}